377
00:33:39,000 --> 00:33:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] I don't even have to drive anywhere.

378
00:33:41,000 --> 00:33:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Više ne moram nigdje nići, ne moram se voziti.

379
00:33:43,000 --> 00:33:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jesus shows up at my house and starts doing miracles.

380
00:33:46,000 --> 00:33:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isus dođe u moju kuću i počne činiti čudesa.

381
00:33:49,000 --> 00:33:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] I like this.

382
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sviđa mi se ovo.

383
00:33:51,000 --> 00:33:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] If this is his lordship, I'm good.

384
00:33:53,000 --> 00:33:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je to njegovo gospodstvo, super.

385
00:33:56,000 --> 00:33:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] The next morning they wake up.

386
00:33:58,000 --> 00:33:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Iduće jutro se probude.

387
00:33:59,000 --> 00:34:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] He's nowhere around.

388
00:34:01,000 --> 00:34:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] They have to go out looking for him.

389
00:34:04,000 --> 00:34:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Moraju izać van i tražiti ga.

390
00:34:06,000 --> 00:34:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] And they finally find him praying.

391
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kad ga napokon nađu kako moli.

392
00:34:11,000 --> 00:34:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] And they say, Jesus, everybody's back at my house.

393
00:34:15,000 --> 00:34:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] We're ready to start the prayer meeting again.

394
00:34:18,000 --> 00:34:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] I dođemo, kažu, Isus, svi su već došli u kuću,

395
00:34:21,000 --> 00:34:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] čekaju da počne molitveni susret.

396
00:34:23,000 --> 00:34:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] We already have everything set.

397
00:34:25,000 --> 00:34:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve već priprenjeno.

398
00:34:26,000 --> 00:34:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] All we need is you.

399
00:34:27,000 --> 00:34:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo tebe čekamo.

400
00:34:28,000 --> 00:34:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] And Jesus says, we're not going back to your house.

401
00:34:31,000 --> 00:34:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isus im kaže, ne vraćamo se u tvoju kuću.

402
00:34:34,000 --> 00:34:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] We're going to another area.

403
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo u drugo područje.

404
00:34:38,000 --> 00:34:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] And you need to leave your house and come with me to the new place.

405
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti moraš ostaviti svoju kuću i ići za mnom u to drugo mjesto.

406
00:34:47,000 --> 00:34:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] Yeah, but everything's ready at my house.

407
00:34:50,000 --> 00:34:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, u mojoj kući je već sve spremno.

408
00:34:53,000 --> 00:34:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] I already made the sandwiches.

409
00:34:55,000 --> 00:34:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Već sam pripremio sandviče.

410
00:34:56,000 --> 00:34:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Everything's good to go.

411
00:34:58,000 --> 00:34:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je spremno da idemo.

412
00:34:59,000 --> 00:35:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] You come back into my world.

413
00:35:02,000 --> 00:35:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti se vrati nazad u moj svijet.

414
00:35:05,000 --> 00:35:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] And Jesus says, no, you come back into my world.

415
00:35:10,000 --> 00:35:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isus kaže, ne.

416
00:35:11,000 --> 00:35:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti se vrati nazad u moj svijet.

417
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] I, Gospodo, Isus, Gospod, je aktivan u našem svijetu danas.

418
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] I jedan dan vam može dat jedno usmjerenje.

419
00:35:35,000 --> 00:35:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] And show you something else on another day.

420
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] A nešto drugo drugog dana.

421
00:35:40,000 --> 00:35:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] And that demands us to humble our hearts.

422
00:35:45,000 --> 00:35:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] I to od nas zahtijeva da ponizimo svoje srca.

423
00:35:48,000 --> 00:35:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] And pay attention.

424
00:35:50,000 --> 00:35:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] I usmjerimo svoju pažnju.

425
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] And to do what he's telling us.

426
00:35:55,000 --> 00:35:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] I učinimo ono što nam on kaže.

427
00:35:57,000 --> 00:36:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] It doesn't always make sense.

428
00:36:00,000 --> 00:36:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] We don't usually understand completely.

429
00:36:05,000 --> 00:36:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Najčešće ne razumijemo u potpunosti.

430
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] But the first step of his lordship is our obedience.

431
00:36:12,000 --> 00:36:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali prvi korak pod njegovim gospodstvom je naša poslušnost.

432
00:36:17,000 --> 00:36:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] And little by little by little.

433
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] I malo po malo.

434
00:36:22,000 --> 00:36:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] We will begin to hear the master's voice.

435
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Počet ćemo čuti učiteljev glas.

436
00:36:28,000 --> 00:36:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] And when we're faithful and obedient in the little things.

437
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kada smo poslušni u malim stvarima i vjerni u malim stvarima.

438
00:36:36,000 --> 00:36:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] The normal things of our everyday life.

439
00:36:39,000 --> 00:36:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Normalne stvari našeg svakodnevnog života.

440
00:36:41,000 --> 00:36:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Budi vjeran u tome.

441
00:36:44,000 --> 00:36:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] And then he'll begin to show us more.

442
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] i on će nam početi pokazivati više.

